# Voice ↔ Bulk Import Parity Analysis

## 1) What Already Works Well (reuse ✅)

| Feature | Bulk | Voice | Notes |
|---|---|---|---|
| Upload + file validation | [InlineDropZone](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/bulk-import/inline-drop-zone.tsx#22-207) | [VoiceInterviewLauncher](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/voice-interview-launcher.tsx#47-397) | Voice has its own CTA, good |
| Inline progress stepper | `InlineImportProgress` | [VoiceProcessingProgress](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/voice-processing-progress.tsx#65-242) | Same pattern, emerald themed |
| Paginated item loading | `bulkImportAPI.listItems` | Same API client | Identical code |
| Partial finalize | [finalize(resolvedGroupIds)](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/lib/api/bulk-import.ts#211-234) | Same endpoint | Backend handles both |
| Success screen | [SuccessAnimation](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/bulk-import/import-review-section.tsx#217-297) | [VoiceSuccessScreen](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/voice-success-screen.tsx#15-80) | Voice version is cleaner |
| Group-level review | [SuggestionCard](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/bulk-import/import-review-section.tsx#1059-1341) per location | [LocationGroupCard](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/location-group-card.tsx#24-141) | Voice adds RadioGroup resolver |
| Status guards | — | [shouldDisableFinalizeAction](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/voice-review-guards.ts#1-15) | Unit tested |
| Transcript + audio | N/A | [TranscriptPanel](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/transcript-panel.tsx#31-223) | Voice-only feature ✅ |

