## 2) Real Gaps (prioritized)

### P0 — Functional parity (blocks real use)

| # | Gap | Bulk has | Voice missing | Risk |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| **G1** | Orphan rescue | [OrphanLocationPicker](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/bulk-import/import-review-section.tsx#302-478) — waste streams without a location can be assigned to an existing location via `Select` | No orphan handling. Streams without `parentItemId` or `groupId` are invisible | **High** — data loss |
| **G2** | Location/stream visual distinction | [SuggestionCard](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/bulk-import/import-review-section.tsx#1059-1341) shows 📍 location header + indented ☑ waste streams per-location | [LocationGroupCard](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/location-group-card.tsx#24-141) title shows `grp_` hash or "Location group"; stream items show "Invalid" with no context | **High** — user confusion (you saw this) |
| **G3** | Full edit drawer | [EditItemDrawer](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/bulk-import/edit-item-drawer.tsx#48-213) — Sheet with labeled fields, description, review notes, validation | [StreamCard](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/stream-card.tsx#53-244) inline edit with 2 small inputs, no field labels, no description, no review notes | **Medium** — limits data correction |

### P1 — UX polish (not blocking but noticeable)

| # | Gap | Bulk has | Voice missing |
|---|---|---|---|
| **G4** | Item-level selection | Checkboxes per waste stream in each location group (toggle inclusion before "Add") | All-or-nothing: accept/reject per stream, but no batch "select which streams to include" before resolving |
| **G5** | Undo after reject/skip | Toast with "Undo" action using [reset](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/voice-interview-launcher.tsx#52-61) API | No undo — reject is final until page reload |
| **G6** | Skeleton loading | [SkeletonCard](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/bulk-import/import-review-section.tsx#186-212) grid with pulse animation | Simple centered spinner |
| **G7** | Duplicate candidate handling | Checkbox "This is a new location" + warning when duplicates detected | Not applicable yet (voice creates via `confirmCreateNew`), but worth noting |

