## 3) Concrete Low-Risk Fixes

### Fix G1 — Orphan rescue in voice

> [!IMPORTANT]
> This is the highest-priority gap. Without it, waste streams the AI extracts but can't match to a location group are silently lost.

#### What to do
Detect orphan items (items with no `groupId` and no `parentItemId`) after loading, and render the existing [OrphanLocationPicker](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/bulk-import/import-review-section.tsx#302-478) from bulk-import.

#### [MODIFY] [voice-review-workspace.tsx](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/voice-review-workspace.tsx)

```diff
+import { OrphanLocationPicker } from "../bulk-import/import-review-section";
 // ... after groups are computed:
+const orphanItems = items.filter(
+  (i) => i.itemType === "project" && !i.groupId && !i.parentItemId
+);
 // ... in JSX, after groups.map():
+{orphanItems.length > 0 && companyLocations && (
+  <OrphanLocationPicker
+    orphanItems={orphanItems}
+    filename="Voice interview"
+    locations={companyLocations}
+    onAssignOrphans={handleAssignOrphans}
+    onDismiss={() => {}}
+  />
+)}
```

> **Prerequisite**: Export [OrphanLocationPicker](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/bulk-import/import-review-section.tsx#302-478) from [import-review-section.tsx](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/bulk-import/import-review-section.tsx) (currently not exported) or extract it to a shared file.

