### Fix G6 — Skeleton loading

#### [MODIFY] [voice-review-workspace.tsx](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/voice-review-workspace.tsx)

Replace spinner with 2–3 skeleton cards matching size of [LocationGroupCard](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/location-group-card.tsx#24-141):

```tsx
if (loading) {
  return (
    <div className="rounded-xl border bg-background">
      {header}
      <div className="space-y-3 p-4">
        {[1, 2, 3].map((i) => (
          <div key={i} className="rounded-lg border p-4 space-y-3 animate-pulse">
            <div className="flex items-center gap-2">
              <div className="h-6 w-6 rounded-full bg-muted" />
              <div className="h-4 w-48 bg-muted rounded" />
            </div>
            <div className="h-16 bg-muted rounded" />
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  );
}
```

