| **G5**: Undo toast on reject | [voice-review-workspace.tsx](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/voice-review-workspace.tsx) | 20 min |
| **G6**: Skeleton loading | [voice-review-workspace.tsx](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/voice-review-workspace.tsx) | 30 min |
| **G3**: Reuse [EditItemDrawer](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/bulk-import/edit-item-drawer.tsx#48-213) | [voice-review-workspace.tsx](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/voice-review-workspace.tsx), [stream-card.tsx](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/stream-card.tsx) | 1 h |

### Phase 2: Structural (1 sprint)

| Task | Files | Effort |
|---|---|---|
| **G1**: Orphan rescue | Extract [OrphanLocationPicker](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/bulk-import/import-review-section.tsx#302-478) to shared, wire in workspace, pass `companyLocations` prop through from company page | 3–4 h |
| **G4**: Item-level checkboxes | [LocationGroupCard](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/location-group-card.tsx#24-141), [voice-review-workspace.tsx](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/voice-review-workspace.tsx) — add `selectedIds` + `onToggleItem` like bulk import | 2–3 h |
| **G7**: Duplicate candidate warning | [LocationGroupCard](file:///Users/ricardoaltamirano/Developer/waste-platform/frontend/components/features/voice-interview/location-group-card.tsx#24-141) — show inline alert when `item.duplicateCandidates?.length > 0` | 1 h |

### Validations to run after each phase

```bash
npx tsc --noEmit             # 0 errors
bun test voice-interview/    # 4/4 pass
# Browser: upload a voice file, verify groups show readable names,
#          reject a stream → see undo toast, check orphan picker if applicable
```
